    "description": "On a system where FIPS 140-2 mode is enabled, <tt>/proc/sys/crypto/fips_enabled</tt> must exist.\nTo verify FIPS mode, run the following command:\n<pre>cat /proc/sys/crypto/fips_enabled</pre>",
